\section{Algorithm and paper deviation}{

Algorithm 2 line 6 of the paper, as literally written
(\verb{v <- -Omega_s * v / ||Omega_s * v||}), estimates \code{-lambda_max(Omega_s)}
rather than \code{lambda_min(Omega_s)}: power iteration on \code{-Omega_s}
